* Download the Haskell platform, version 2014.2.0.0
* Run 'cabal update'
* Run 'cabal install cabal-install' (may take some time)
* Make sure that invoking 'cabal --version' indicates that you are using version 1.20.* of cabal
* Make sure that you are using alex and happy from the platform (and not some older versions in your PATH)
* Run 'cabal sandbox init'
* Run 'cabal install --only-dependencies'
* Run './prepare'
